Subject: drm/amdgpu: Add flag to wipe VRAM on release
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d8f4981e2e8a968411105db568f3d48256b2ebbc
